{
  "id": "p0-openclaw-inline-choice",
  "title": "OpenClaw inline clarify card sends plain chat choice",
  "tags": ["p0", "openclaw", "choice", "ui"],
  "setup": {
    "serverMode": "openclaw",
    "accountId": "e2e_mock",
    "agentName": "E2E Mock OpenClaw",
    "httpPort": 18780,
    "upstreamPort": 18766,
    "mediaPort": 18781
  },
  "steps": [
    { "action": "launch_app" },
    { "action": "create_conversation", "name": "E2E OpenClaw Choice" },
    { "action": "send_message", "text": "测试 OpenClaw 内联选择" },
    { "action": "wait_for_text", "text": "你希望使用哪种编程语言？" },
    { "action": "wait_for_key", "key": "ui_e2e_inline_clarify_card" },
    { "action": "tap_key", "key": "ui_e2e_inline_clarify_choice_TypeScript" },
    { "action": "wait_for_text", "text": "OpenClaw 已收到选择：TypeScript" }
  ],
  "mockGateway": {
    "interactions": [
      {
        "on": { "type": "chat", "contains": "测试 OpenClaw 内联选择" },
        "replies": [
          {
            "type": "agent_text_delta",
            "message_id": "agent_msg_openclaw_choice_1",
            "delta": "在开始之前，我需要确认一些信息：\n\n```clarify\nquestion: 你希望使用哪种编程语言？\nchoices:\n- Python\n- TypeScript\n- Rust\n- Go\n```\n\n请选择一个选项。"
          },
          {
            "type": "agent_text_done",
            "message_id": "agent_msg_openclaw_choice_1",
            "fullText": "在开始之前，我需要确认一些信息：\n\n```clarify\nquestion: 你希望使用哪种编程语言？\nchoices:\n- Python\n- TypeScript\n- Rust\n- Go\n```\n\n请选择一个选项。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "on": { "type": "chat", "equals": "TypeScript" },
        "replies": [
          {
            "type": "agent_text_delta",
            "message_id": "agent_msg_openclaw_choice_2",
            "delta": "OpenClaw 已收到选择：TypeScript"
          },
          {
            "type": "agent_text_done",
            "message_id": "agent_msg_openclaw_choice_2",
            "fullText": "OpenClaw 已收到选择：TypeScript"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "assert": [
    { "uiTextVisible": "OpenClaw 已收到选择：TypeScript" }
  ]
}
